text: Irène Pittelioen (13 May 1927 - 21 August 2011) was a French gymnast. She competed at the 1948 Summer Olympics and the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1927 births Category:2011 deaths Category:French female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of France Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Lille
